title: Tangled Web
description: In this Dateline classic, investigators discover a twisted tale of secrets, lies and infidelity after a beloved firefighter is murdered just outside Sarasota, Florida. Andrea Canning reports. Originally aired on NBC on February 5, 2016.
author: nbcnews.podcasts@gmail.com (NBC News)
